hopobject.body: How do you do? prematurex australia Everyone knows it is easier to train for and run a long distance with motivation from a like-minded running partner. You could become the Bupa buddy of one member of Team Telegraph, training for and running with them in one of the following events: the Bupa Great North Run (half marathon), the Bupa Great South Run (10 miles), the Bupa Great North 5k or the Bupa Great Yorkshire Run (10k).
